"title": "7025: church, unity and fellowship of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "7025",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The church is one in essence, because it is founded on one gospel, united to one Lord and indwelt by one Spirit. Its unity is under constant threat because of the tendency to division that is inherent in fallen humanity, and needs to be continually maintained and actively expressed in fellowship.</p>\n<h2>The unity of the church</h2>\n<h3>The church is one</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:5\">ROM 12:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor12:12\">1CO 12:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor12:20\">1CO 12:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:25\">EPH 4:25</a></p>\n<h3>The church transcends all barriers</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:11\">COL 3:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:16\">JHN 10:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:28-Acts10:29\">ACT 10:28–10:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:47\">ACT 10:47</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts15:8-Acts15:9\">ACT 15:8–15:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal3:28\">GAL 3:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:14-Eph2:16\">EPH 2:14–2:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph3:6\">EPH 3:6</a> <em>The great divide threatening the first Christians was between Jew and Gentile, but the church was able to unite the two into one body in Christ.</em></p>\n<h3>The church's unity reflects the unity within the Trinity</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:4-Eph4:6\">EPH 4:4–4:6</a></strong> <em>The unity of the church is built around the persons of the Trinity: one Spirit, one Lord, one Father.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:11\">JHN 17:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom3:29-Rom3:30\">ROM 3:29–3:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom10:12-Rom10:13\">ROM 10:12–10:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal3:27-Gal3:28\">GAL 3:27–3:28</a></p>\n<h3>The church's unity is the work of the Trinity</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:16-Eph2:18\">EPH 2:16–2:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John11:52\">JHN 11:52</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:45-Acts10:47\">ACT 10:45–10:47</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor12:13\">1CO 12:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:22\">EPH 2:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:3\">EPH 4:3</a></p>\n<h2>The purpose of the church's unity</h2>\n<h3>To lead others to faith</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:23\">JHN 17:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:21\">JHN 17:21</a></p>\n<h3>To lead believers to maturity</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:13\">EPH 4:13</a></strong></p>\n<h2>The nature of the church's unity</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:1-Phil2:2\">PHP 2:1–2:2</a></strong> <em>Emphasis is placed on an inner unity of mind and spirit rather than external uniformity.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor13:11\">2CO 13:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil1:27\">PHP 1:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col2:2\">COL 2:2</a></p>\n<h2>Appeals for unity in the church</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:3\">EPH 4:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:10\">ROM 12:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:5\">ROM 15:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:7\">ROM 15:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor12:25\">1CO 12:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:14\">COL 3:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet3:8\">1PE 3:8</a></p>\n<h2>The church's unity is expressed in fellowship</h2>\n<h3>Fellowship with God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor1:9\">1CO 1:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor13:14\">2CO 13:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:1\">PHP 2:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet1:4\">2PE 1:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John1:3\">1JN 1:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John1:6-1John1:7\">1JN 1:6–1:7</a></p>\n<h3>Fellowship expressed by meeting together</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:46\">ACT 2:46</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:1\">ACT 2:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:42\">ACT 2:42</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:12\">ACT 5:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts6:2\">ACT 6:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor14:26\">1CO 14:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:25\">HEB 10:25</a></p>\n<h3>Fellowship expressed through sharing resources</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:44-Acts2:45\">ACT 2:44–2:45</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:32\">ACT 4:32</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:34-Acts4:37\">ACT 4:34–4:37</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts11:27-Acts11:30\">ACT 11:27–11:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:26\">ROM 15:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor16:1-1Cor16:2\">1CO 16:1–16:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor8:2-2Cor8:5\">2CO 8:2–8:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor8:13-2Cor8:14\">2CO 8:13–8:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor9:13\">2CO 9:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil4:14-Phil4:18\">PHP 4:14–4:18</a></p>\n<h3>Fellowship through suffering</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev1:9\">REV 1:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:17\">ROM 8:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor1:7\">2CO 1:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil3:10\">PHP 3:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil4:14\">PHP 4:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:33-Heb10:34\">HEB 10:33–10:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb13:3\">HEB 13:3</a></p>\n<h3>Fellowship through shared spiritual blessings</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor9:23\">1CO 9:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom11:17\">ROM 11:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil1:7\">PHP 1:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess2:14\">2TH 2:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet5:1\">1PE 5:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jude1:3\">JUD 1:3</a></p>\n<h2>Specific actions which express fellowship and unity in the church</h2>\n<h3>Sharing in the Lord's Supper</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor10:16-1Cor10:17\">1CO 10:16–10:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:46\">ACT 2:46</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts20:7\">ACT 20:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor11:33\">1CO 11:33</a></p>\n<h3>Baptism as an expression of unity</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:4-Eph4:6\">EPH 4:4–4:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor12:13\">1CO 12:13</a></p>\n<h3>Extending hospitality</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts28:7\">ACT 28:7</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:13\">ROM 12:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom16:23\">ROM 16:23</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim5:10\">1TI 5:10</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus1:8\">TIT 1:8</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet4:9\">1PE 4:9</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/3John1:8\">3JN 1:8</a></p>\n<h3>Greeting one another</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts18:27\">ACT 18:27</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom16:3-Rom16:16\">ROM 16:3–16:16</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor16:19-1Cor16:20\">1CO 16:19–16:20</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col4:10\">COL 4:10</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phlm1:17\">PHM 1:17</a></p>\n<h3>Welcoming former opponents</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:26-Acts9:27\">ACT 9:26–9:27</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal2:9\">GAL 2:9</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor2:5-2Cor2:8\">2CO 2:5–2:8</a></p>\n<h2>Divisions in the church</h2>\n<h3>Causes of division in the NT church</h3>\n<p>Personal ambition:\n <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark9:34\">MRK 9:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:35-Mark10:41\">MRK 10:35–10:41</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt20:20-Matt20:24\">MAT 20:20–20:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts6:1\">ACT 6:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts15:37-Acts15:40\">ACT 15:37–15:40</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil4:2\">PHP 4:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom16:17\">ROM 16:17</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jude1:19\">JUD 1:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor1:11-1Cor1:12\">1CO 1:11–1:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor3:3-1Cor3:4\">1CO 3:3–3:4</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor6:1-1Cor6:6\">1CO 6:1–6:6</a> <em>litigation and disputes</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor11:18\">1CO 11:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor11:20-1Cor11:21\">1CO 11:20–11:21</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas4:1-Jas4:3\">JAS 4:1–4:3</a></p>\n<h3>Warnings against divisions in the church</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor1:10\">1CO 1:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:16\">ROM 12:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom16:17\">ROM 16:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor12:20\">2CO 12:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:31\">EPH 4:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas4:11\">JAS 4:11</a></p>\n<h3>Acceptable differences in the church</h3>\n<p>In secondary matters of conscience, Christians are to respect rather than judge each other. These things need not impair the essential unity that is in Christ:\n <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom14:1-Rom14:3\">ROM 14:1–14:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom14:5-Rom14:6\">ROM 14:5–14:6</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor8:9-1Cor8:13\">1CO 8:9–8:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor12:4-1Cor12:6\">1CO 12:4–12:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor12:14-1Cor12:25\">1CO 12:14–12:25</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal2:7\">GAL 2:7</a></p>\n<h3>Necessary divisions in the church</h3>\n<p>Between the true gospel and heretical alternatives:\n <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor11:2-2Cor11:6\">2CO 11:2–11:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor11:13-2Cor11:15\">2CO 11:13–11:15</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal1:6-Gal1:9\">GAL 1:6–1:9</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col2:8\">COL 2:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col2:16-Col2:19\">COL 2:16–2:19</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim4:1-1Tim4:6\">1TI 4:1–4:6</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John2:18-1John2:19\">1JN 2:18–2:19</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2John1:9-2John1:11\">2JN 1:9–1:11</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jude1:18-Jude1:20\">JUD 1:18–1:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor5:9-1Cor5:10\">1CO 5:9–5:10</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess3:6\">2TH 3:6</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:3-1Tim6:5\">1TI 6:3–6:5</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim3:2-2Tim3:9\">2TI 3:2–3:9</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet1:20-2Pet1:21\">2PE 1:20–1:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet2:1-2Pet2:3\">2PE 2:1–2:3</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:20\">REV 2:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:24\">REV 2:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev3:1\">REV 3:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev3:4\">REV 3:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts15:2\">ACT 15:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts15:5-Acts15:6\">ACT 15:5–15:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts15:19\">ACT 15:19</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal2:11\">GAL 2:11</a></p>",
